        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A short energy statement for when guilt about thriving is present. The statement holds both truths: what they went through was real, and your ease doesn't diminish it.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to energy statements? Read ",
